'''艾瑞克·貝達德'''（{{lang-en|Érik Joseph Bédard}}，（{{bd|1979年|3月5日}}）出生於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]的[[渥太華|渥太華]]，曾是[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[先發投手|先發投手]]。

貝達德初登版的球隊為[[巴爾的摩金鶯|巴爾的摩金鶯]]，當時為球隊倚賴的[[先發投手|先發投手]]，2007年時其每9局可以投出10.93次的三振<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3237189 |title=Orioles trade Bedard to Mariners for five prospects |accessdate=November 26, 2008 |author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=February 9, 2008 |work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]] |archive-date=2016-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110115756/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3237189 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年交易到[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]，之後又在2011年被交易到[[波士頓紅襪|波士頓紅襪]]。

==職業生涯==
===巴爾的摩金鶯===
[[File:091306_034_Érik_Bédard.jpg|220px]] in 2006]]
貝達德在[[巴爾的摩金鶯|巴爾的摩金鶯]]共待了4年球季的時間，為左投的先發投手。在2007年擔任金鶯的開幕戰投手。5月20日，在對[[華盛頓國民|華盛頓國民]]的跨聯盟比賽中，擊出生涯的第1支安打，在下一個打席不但擊出安打，還得到生涯的第1分打點。7月7日對德州遊騎兵的比賽中，他投出了15次的三振，平了球隊[[麥克·穆西納|麥克·穆西納]]所保持的紀錄。

===西雅圖水手===
[[File:Érik_Bédard_signs_autographs.jpg|200px]]
2008年2月8日，[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]以外野手[[亞當·瓊斯|亞當·瓊斯]]、投手George Sherrill等共5名球員，和金鶯交易貝達德<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080208&content_id=2368497&vkey=hotstove2007&fext=.jsp |title=Mariners seal deal for Bedard Fireballing lefty arrives as Seattle sends five players to O's |accessdate=November 26, 2008 |last=Street |first=Jim |date=February 8, 2008 |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2009-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804061131/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080208&content_id=2368497&vkey=hotstove2007&fext=.jsp |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在之後的2月13日，總教練John McLaren宣布貝達德為球隊的開幕戰先發投手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080213&content_id=2372254&vkey=spt2008news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Bedard named Opening Day starter Experience determining factor over Hernandez |accessdate=November 26, 2008 |last=Street |first=Jim |date=February 13, 2008 |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023053807/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080213&content_id=2372254&vkey=spt2008news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月15日，水手和貝達德簽下1年700萬美金的合約，雙方避免薪資仲裁<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080215&content_id=2374829&vkey=spt2008news&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |title=Bedard inks one-year deal with Mariners Left-hander obtained in trade with Orioles in early February |accessdate=November 26, 2008 |last=Street |first=Jim |date=February 15, 2008 |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2012-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208114936/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080215&content_id=2374829&vkey=spt2008news&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月19日，因傷被球隊放進傷兵名單<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080709&content_id=3101242&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |title=Bedard might miss DL with Batista injury Right-hander leaves game against A's in third inning |accessdate=November 26, 2008 |last=Street |first=Jim |date=July 10, 2008 |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225002354/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080709&content_id=3101242&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年，貝達德在幫球隊投了4個月的比賽以後，就因傷再度進入傷兵名單，這一年他繳出5勝3敗和2.82防禦率的成績，在球季結束以後球隊選擇不續約而變成自由球員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091106&content_id=7634204&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |title=Bedard, Batista, Chavez opt for free agency |accessdate=November 7, 2009 |last=Street |first=Jim |date=November 6, 2009 |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2014-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416181428/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091106&content_id=7634204&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年2月6日，水手和貝達德簽下1年包括2011年球隊選擇權的合約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100206&content_id=8032282&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea|title=Mariners bring back lefty Bedard|accessdate=February 7, 2010|last=Street|first=Jim|date=February 6, 2010|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|archive-date=2012-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324132342/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100206&content_id=8032282&vkey=news_sea&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但這一年貝達德因傷完全沒有出賽的紀錄。

2011年，水手買斷貝達德的合約，而重新和他簽下合約<ref>{{cite news | url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2013581160_mariners_sign_erik_bedard_to_a.html | work=The Seattle Times | first=Geoff | last=Baker | title=Mariners sign Erik Bedard to a one-year deal | date=December 2, 2010 | accessdate=2011-08-02 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629071535/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2013581160_mariners_sign_erik_bedard_to_a.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===波士頓紅襪=== 
2011年7月31日，[[波士頓紅襪|波士頓紅襪]] 以小聯盟球員[[蔣智賢|蔣智賢]]經由三方交易（包括[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]）獲得水手的投手貝達德和道奇的Josh Fields<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110731&content_id=22559672&vkey=news_bos&c_id=bos |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110801231550/http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110731&content_id=22559672&vkey=news_bos&c_id=bos |archivedate=2011-08-01 }}</ref>。

